dSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013171, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "All praise be to Allah Who has guided us to this; and we would not have found the way had it not been that Allah had guided us. All praise be to Allah Who has made me travel in His countries, Who has caused me to ride His animals, Who has made the distant space seem near for me, Who has kept away from me what is dangerous, and Who has held off against me what is unwanted until He made me come up to the Precinct of the brother of His Messenger, peace be upon him and his Household.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Hamd Khuda ke liye hai jis ne hamein raasta dikhaaya aur agar Woh rehbari na farmaata to ham hidaayat yaafta na ho sakte thay. Hamd Khuda ke liye hai jis ne mujhe shehro’n se guzaara apne chopaayo’n par sawaari karaayi, dur ki musaafat (safar) taiy karne ki taufiq di, rukaawate rafa (dur) farmaayi aur buraayi ko mujh se dur rakkha yahan tak keh mai uske Rasool ke baraadar (bhai) ki baargah mein pohonch gaya hu.", "Urdu": "حمد خدا کے لئے ہے جس نے ہمیں راستہ دکھایا اور اگر وہ رہبری نہ فرماتا تو ہم ہدایت یافتہ نہ ہو سکتے تھے حمد خدا کے لئے ہے جس نےمجھے شہروں سے گزارااپنے چوپایوں پر سواری کرائی دور کی مسافت طے کرنے کی توفیق دی رکاوٹیں ختم فرمائیں اور برائی کو مجھ سے دور رکھا یہاں تک کہ میں اس کے رسول ﷺ کے برادر کی بارگاہ میں پہنچ گیا ہوں۔", "RArabic": "ALHAMDO LILLAA-HIL LAZEE HADAANAA LEHAAZAA WA MAA KUNNAA LE-NAH-TA-DEYA LAWLAA AN HADAA-NAL LAAHO. ALHAMDO LILLAA-HIL LAZEE SAYYA-RANEE FEE BELAA-DEHI WA HAMA-LANEE ’ALAA DAWAAAB-BEHI WA TAWAA LE-YAL BA-’EEDA WA SARAFA ’ANNIL MAHZOORA WA DAFA’A ’ANNIL MAKROOHA HATTAA AQDAMANEE HARAMA AKHEE RASOOLEHI SALLAL LAAHO A’LAIHE WA AALEHI.", "ArabicText1": "اَلْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الَّذِیْ هَدَانَا لِهٰذَا وَمَا كُنَّا لِنَهْتَدِیَ لَوْلَا اَنْ هَدٰانَا اللهُ، اَلْحَمْدُ لِلهِ الَّذِیْ سَیَّرَنِیْ فِیْ بِلَادِهٖ وَحَمَلَنِیْ عَلٰی دَوَآبِّهٖ وَطَوٰی لِیَ الْبَعِیْدَ وَصَرَفَ عَنِّیْ الْمَحْذُوْرَ وَدَفَعَ عَنِّیْ الْمَكْرُوْهَ حَتّٰی اَقْدَمَنِیْ حَرَمَ اَخِیْ رَسُوْلِهٖ صَلَّی اللهُ عَلَیْهِ وَاٰلِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "Arabi